  "category": "Uncategorized",
  "description": "Fix Breadcrumb Alignment on Subpages\n\nCorrect the visual alignment issues in breadcrumb navigation where icons and text elements are misaligned on subpages.\n\nRequirements:\n- Identify breadcrumb components used across subpages\n- Verify SVG icon display properties and set to inline or inline-block as needed\n- Adjust vertical alignment of icons to match text baseline\n- Ensure consistent spacing between icon and text elements\n- Test alignment across different breadcrumb depths and text lengths\n- Verify fix works consistently across all subpages using breadcrumbs\n\nSpecific alignment adjustments:\n- Set proper CSS display property for SVG elements (likely display: inline or inline-block)\n- Adjust vertical-align property to center or text-bottom for icon-text alignment\n- Consider adding flexbox/grid alignment if container needs restructuring\n- Maintain consistent visual rhythm with appropriate margins/padding",
